        <mxCell id="Yp-4mwVo2HuiF391OTCQ-1" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="design a hotstar like application with following requirements&amp;nbsp;&lt;div&gt;1. User login Services&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;2. Subscribe Services&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;3. Movie/TV show Search Service&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;4. Movie / TV show play Servic.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Optimize the application using CDC pipeline, highlight where proxy design pattern can be used.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Use HLS and DASH for specific live/static content playing along with manifest file&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
